definitions.definition: Decorative paper -like material used to cover the inner walls of buildings.
A style or design of such material.
examples: He is letting her select the wallpapers for the whole house.

definitions.definition: Anything that serves as a background or part of the surroundings .
An image or tiled pattern used as the background of a computer desktop .
examples: He chose a Minecraft design as his computer's wallpaper .

definitions.definition: Generic footage of a building or location that may be used in the background of a related news report.
Gaudy mass-produced stamps, typically of little or no value and only produced for sale to collectors.
A radio operator's collection of awards and QSL cards .

main_definition: ( uncountable ) Decorative paper -like material used to cover the inner walls of buildings.
secondary_definitions: ( countable ) A roll of such paper.
( countable ) A style or design of such material.
( uncountable , figurative , sometimes attributive ) Anything that serves as a background or part of the surroundings .
( computing , countable , uncountable ) An image or tiled pattern used as the background of a computer desktop .
( television , slang ) Generic footage of a building or location that may be used in the background of a related news report.
( philately , informal ) Gaudy mass-produced stamps, typically of little or no value and only produced for sale to collectors.
( CB radio slang ) A radio operator's collection of awards and QSL cards .
